Package: r2bb
Title: Construct Blackboard LMS tests and questions with R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Bertolacci", , "michael.bertolacci@uwa.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0317-5941"))
Description: This package provides a set of functions to construct Blackboard LMS tests and questions with R. These can be converted to zipped XML files that can be imported into Blackboard.
